{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-08",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友大家好，欢迎收听AI每日先锋，今天是2026年7月8日。我是苏晴。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 8.446,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是周航。苏晴你今天声音听着挺轻快，是不是有什么好消息？",
      "start": 9.895,
      "duration": 5.747,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那可不，最近WAIC刚结束，料多到我想加播两期。先说最让我震撼的一个事儿——AI现在不光是帮你算东西了，它开始自己\"做科学\"了。",
      "start": 16.139,
      "duration": 14.324,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你说的是AI4S这个方向吧？我前两天看量子位的稿子，说得很到位。以前的AI在科研里就是个计算器，你扔数据进去它给你跑结果。但现在不一样了，AI能自己提出假设，自己设计实验路径，最后自己验证。",
      "start": 30.916,
      "duration": 17.652,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，这个\"自主发现\"的提法我觉得特别关键。以前AlphaFold那种已经很厉害了，但它本质上还是人类给定问题、AI去求解。现在这波范式转变，AI是要从头到尾参与科学发现的全流程。",
      "start": 48.973,
      "duration": 18.871,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，这个转变背后其实是中国的一次系统性布局。WAIC上展示的不只是某一项技术突破，而是整个科研基础设施的搭建——从数据平台、模型底座到跨学科联盟，全链路都在往前推。",
      "start": 68.277,
      "duration": 17.521,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这个意义比单纯发一个模型大太多了。你想想，如果AI真能成为科研的\"合作者\"而不只是工具，那药物研发、材料科学、气候变化这些领域的研究效率会被指数级拉升。",
      "start": 86.263,
      "duration": 16.999,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "没错。而且这里面有个更深层的东西——标准和生态。谁先跑通这条路，谁就掌握了下游所有科研应用的接口定义权。这不是赢一场比赛的问题，是定义赛道的问题。",
      "start": 103.724,
      "duration": 12.582,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "说白了，谁先把工具链搭好，别的国家的科研团队就自然会用你的标准，到时候切换成本高得吓人。中国这次在WAIC上打的明显就是这个主意。",
      "start": 116.757,
      "duration": 13.279,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，而且这事儿跟咱们普通人也不是没关系。你可能觉得AI搞科研离自己很远，但你想啊——以后新药研发周期从十年缩短到两三年，新能源材料从实验室到量产加速，这些变化最终都会落到咱们的生活里。",
      "start": 130.536,
      "duration": 18.392,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "说到这个，我还想聊WAIC上另一个让我特别兴奋的——理论基础层面的突破。周航你研究过\"数理双向赋能\"这个概念吗？",
      "start": 149.366,
      "duration": 11.668,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "看了。说实话前几年大家都在卷模型规模、卷数据量、卷算力，但很少有人去碰底层理论。中国学界这次提的\"数理双向赋能\"，意思是用数学和物理的基本原理去双向校准AI的架构演进。",
      "start": 161.495,
      "duration": 16.999,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "等等我没太听明白，能再展开说说吗？什么叫\"双向\"赋能？",
      "start": 178.939,
      "duration": 5.573,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "简单说就是两条腿走路。一条腿是用更前沿的数学理论——比如范畴论、拓扑学这些——去给AI架构找新的数学根基；另一条腿是反过来，让AI去帮物理学家、化学家做基础研究，反哺科学本身。",
      "start": 184.986,
      "duration": 17.521,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦这么一说我懂了！这不就是把AI和基础科学从\"应用关系\"变成\"共生关系\"嘛。",
      "start": 202.934,
      "duration": 6.792,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你这个总结比很多论文摘要都到位。问题的关键在于，如果这条路走通，下一代大模型的能力天花板会被彻底重写——它不再是靠堆参数堆出来的，而是有数学原理和物理规律双重锚定的全新架构。",
      "start": 210.19,
      "duration": 16.259,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这种理论突破一旦成型，影响的是未来5到10年的技术基调。比发一百个新模型都重要，因为它是定义下一阶段游戏规则的。",
      "start": 226.866,
      "duration": 12.278,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "是这样。而且你想啊，现在大模型很多现象——涌现、幻觉、泛化能力——咱们其实说不清楚为什么。如果数理双向赋能这条路能把这些黑箱打开，那对整个行业都是质变。",
      "start": 239.58,
      "duration": 15.717,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "说白了，就是从\"能用\"到\"知其所以然\"的跨越。中国学界这个押注我觉得挺有魄力的，毕竟基础研究见效慢，但一旦突破就是全局性的。",
      "start": 255.714,
      "duration": 14.237,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对。所以你看今年WAIC其实传递了一个很清晰的信号——中国AI的竞争主战场正在从\"应用层\"上移到\"基础设施和基础理论\"层。这是战略级别的转向。",
      "start": 270.447,
      "duration": 12.408,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，格局完全不一样了。对了，说完大的，来聊几个最近的产品更新吧，不然听众朋友说我俩光顾着仰望星空了。",
      "start": 283.267,
      "duration": 9.665,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哈哈好。先说Google，Gemini API这次对Managed Agents做了大幅扩展，新增了后台任务和远程MCP支持。",
      "start": 293.411,
      "duration": 9.622,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这个更新对企业用户太关键了。以前用Agent最头疼的就是——你让它干活，它得一直占着连接，断一下就崩了。现在后台任务一支持，相当于给Agent配了个独立工位，干活的时候不用你盯着。",
      "start": 303.465,
      "duration": 18.392,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你这个比喻很形象。补充一个技术点——远程MCP的意思是Agent可以直接调用远端部署的工具和服务，不限于本地。这下Agent的网络化能力算是补齐了。",
      "start": 322.325,
      "duration": 11.712,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，Google这波其实是在给企业级Agent铺路。你想啊，未来每个公司可能都会有几十个Agent协同干活，没有可靠的基础设施根本撑不住。",
      "start": 334.527,
      "duration": 11.363,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说到Agent基建，智谱这边也没闲着。GLM-5.2发布了，主打长时程任务能力。你注意啊，这个\"长时程\"是关键词——以前的模型做三步五步的任务还行，再多就开始丢三落四。",
      "start": 346.367,
      "duration": 15.344,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对我特别有感触。我之前用一些Agent工具做复杂任务，经常做到一半它就把前面的上下文忘了，或者跑偏到完全不相干的地方，特别崩溃。",
      "start": 362.129,
      "duration": 12.103,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "GLM-5.2这次就是冲着这个痛点来的。强化的是持续规划和长链条执行能力，本质上是在为复杂的多步骤Agent工作流打底座。",
      "start": 374.671,
      "duration": 12.452,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这也说明一个问题——现在模型光\"聪明\"已经不够了，还得\"能扛事儿\"。Agent时代对模型的综合素养要求又上了一个台阶。",
      "start": 387.535,
      "duration": 12.234,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "没错。还有个挺好玩的消息，HuggingFace搞了个Agentic Resource Discovery——让Agent能自己去搜索工具、技能甚至其他Agent。",
      "start": 400.262,
      "duration": 10.294,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "真的假的？这个有点意思。意思是我不用提前给Agent配好所有工具，它能自己上网找？",
      "start": 410.965,
      "duration": 7.619,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，本质上是构建一个Agent可以自主探索的资源网络。你想啊，未来Agent数量爆炸式增长，光靠人工给每个Agent配置资源根本不可能，必须让它能自我扩展。",
      "start": 419.071,
      "duration": 13.932,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个方向我特别看好。它本质上是在解决Agent生态的\"可发现性\"问题——就像早期互联网有了搜索引擎才真正爆发一样，Agent生态也得有这么一层。",
      "start": 433.445,
      "duration": 13.018,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你这个类比很准。说白了就是给Agent修路，把信息孤岛打通。这三个产品更新放在一起看，其实都在为Agent时代的基础设施添砖加瓦。",
      "start": 446.923,
      "duration": 12.06,
