        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，今天聊下来感觉信息量确实大。从WAIC的范式革新到三大厂的Agent基建，整个AI行业正在从\"模型竞争\"走向\"生态竞争\"。",
      "start": 459.454,
      "duration": 14.367,
